A state of silence
============================================
Every instance in this universe streaming(transformation and transmission) is in silence only. Silence is the nature of light energy. In fact Energy always exists in light state of streaming only,
The energy streaming within human brain is also in light state only but it seems to be stressed some time this is due to non awareness about the state of energy. If you have proper awareness about the sate of energy streaming in brain then it never realize you stressed.

Why you do not feel stressed when you have awareness?
-------------------------------
In the state of awareness you attention is not on what is happening there but your attention is to just look lightly the processing of energy. When your attention is looking the 
processing, then it not get stuck but it streaming with the process of streaming of energy. In other words your attention is flowing with streaming ie both streaming together.

When your attention get stuck somewhere in streaming the energy within brain, the streaming of energy within brain not get stuck with your attention but your attention get stuck with some state of energy streaming in brain.
If fact your attention searching something there and taking rotation to search. At this place even you not feel any stress if you rotate lightly ie with awareness but tightly searching become rigid and making us feel stressed.

