At this state when your silence is just going to break you will get an alert. At this state when people know your are in silence you feel good in crowd.
You may realize to keep more and more in since state. At this state you thought gating communication with your inner intelligence system. You may feel little healing in your life.
At this state the energy at your bottom get transmission towards top. At this is state you may plane for silence.
Slowly slowly the silence get dense and move in next zone.

